name: cognify
description: Concussions are some of the most serious injuries seen in high school and collegiate sports. According to the CDC, [11.9% of US high school students](https://www.statista.com/statistics/1448795/us-high-school-students-who-had-a-sports-related-concussion/) reported receiving a concussion from sports in 2021 alone (over 1.5 million people).
